W-What are you doing right now?

4
00:01:43,420 --> 00:01:45,810
What did you do to my lips?

5
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:49,130
Why would you ask?

6
00:01:49,130 --> 00:01:51,380
You're embarrassing me.

7
